				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/D%E1%BA%A1-tr%C3%BA-Gia-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-K0C9ifuOfqkxmZQmhZr0fw">Dạ trú Gia Định - 夜住嘉定</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/D%C4%A9nh-Ch%C3%A2u-l%C3%A3o-%C3%B4ng-ca/poem-sMaN29nfwosLLi7BpB4dYg">Dĩnh Châu lão ông ca - 穎州老翁歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/author-0SVWGWsIUnN7yr-6nBm82Q">Nạp Tân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%E1%BB%87n-Thu%E1%BA%ADt/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tri-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%AD-ti%E1%BA%BFt/poem-4v9kRYaWHu6GmZ8c22UQKg">Điếu Nguyễn Tri Phương tử tiết - 悼阮知方死節</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%E1%BB%87n-Thu%E1%BA%ADt/author-yymqs1KI3fdivUUn-pVUSw">Nguyễn Thiện Thuật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/H%E1%BB%93-gi%C3%A0-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-01-ph%C3%A1ch/poem-ckVrrZFkNNGZTFO-W9K3Yw">Hồ già thập bát phách - đệ 01 phách - 胡笳十八拍－第一拍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/K%E1%BA%BF-giai-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-trung/poem-WrLWcBYPW8csXCDMgI5nNQ">Kế giai đồ trung - 計偕途中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/author-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Vương Thế Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Sinh-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-Yg2BsJ79o27Uc2SAwQ0Iiw">Sinh tử - 生死</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-1OSMIAchRr0KS69eud03Ug">Giới Không thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.ne